Day 61: Init Containers in Kubernetes

Date: October 30, 2025
Overview
Used init containers for pod initialization tasks.
Key Concepts Learned

Init container pattern
Sequential execution
Dependency management
Initialization workflows

Commands Used
yamlinitContainers:
- name: init-mydb
  image: busybox
  command: ['sh', '-c', 'until nslookup mydb; do sleep 2; done']

Challenges Faced
Debugging init container failures and ensuring they completed successfully before main containers started.
